{"tid":1800362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 玫瑰崗 95年 小一 陳姓女班長","createTime":"2019-12-27T17:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:21:50.000Z","uid":36927,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd21098e8095822363289a1947f8bca4d81ac34f","tid":1800362,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"我係當年 (唔記得 1i 定 1j 班) 個副班長啊<br />\n想搵返陳班長<br />\n當年個班主任係Miss Chow<br />\n個日我地私定終身<br />\n你仲話會返黎搵我<br />\n但你之後去咗外國讀書<br />\n我就轉咗校<br />\n然後終於沒終於<br />\n呢件事咁多年黎我一直都耿耿於懷<br />\n今年黎到咗三十而立既年紀<br />\n我好想再見你一面<br />\n同你揮手寒喧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7565ab60ae7b7defc41c6fd35517e76bd72e7d08","tid":1800362,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"幫pish"},{"pid":"a50ac3671b926a0cc9e93b91219e140b154b6381","tid":1800362,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c28c49ed9de07e5aefd02413c4a80e6a5e9a0b","tid":1800362,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a50ac3671b926a0cc9e93b91219e140b154b6381","tid":1800362,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ef0dd2a11d77a20aa859c9f1ca4d9e03677546","tid":1800362,"uid":36927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7565ab60ae7b7defc41c6fd35517e76bd72e7d08","tid":1800362,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"幫pish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"但你不推文回覆"},{"pid":"b853d2c9e9225ec9fec0c02260762893c9742b03","tid":1800362,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco